NAME

    App::MatrixTool - commands to interact with a Matrix home-server

SYNOPSIS

    Usually this would be used via the matrixtool command

     $ matrixtool server-key matrix.org

DESCRIPTION

    Provides the base class and basic level support for commands that
    interact with a Matrix home-server. See individual command modules,
    found under the App::MatrixTool::Command:: namespace, for details on
    specific commands.

AUTHOR

    Paul Evans <leonerd@leonerd.org.uk>

